revisions.description: Added chassis identification objects.
Added following new traps for chassis alarm conditions: jnxFruFailed, jnxFruOffline and jnxFruOnline.
Added new traps for chassis alarm condition jnxFruCheck.
Added new fru type FEB in jnxFruType enumeration.
Added new offline reason pfeVersionMismatch to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reason fruFebOffline to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added jnxBoxSystemDomainType object.
Added new fru type PSD to jnxFruType enumeration and added jcsX chassis IDs to JnxChassisId enumeration.
Added nodeX chassis IDs to JnxChassisId enumeration.
Added sfcX and lcc4-lcc15 chassis IDs to JnxChassisId enumeration.
Added load average variables
Added jnxBoxPersonality for MidRangius Boxes namely MX40/MX10/MX5
Added new offline reason builtinPicBounce to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new jnxFruType: PDU and PSM, and new traps: jnxFmLinkErr and jnxFmCellDropErr.
Added new offline reason fruTypeConfigMismatch to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reason fruTypeConfigMismatch to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reason fruPICOfflineOnEccErrors to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reasons fruFpcIncompatible and fruFpcFanTrayPEMIncompatible to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reason openflowConfigChange to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reasons fruFpcScbIncompatible to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reason hwError to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reasons fruReUnresponsive to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new Fabric plane offline/online/check traps to trap fabric plane offline/online/fault events.
Added new offline reason hwError to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reason fruIncompatibleWithPEM, fruIncompatibleWithSIB, and sibIncompatibleWithOtherSIB to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new offline reason fruPfeErrors to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new OIDs to get control plane memory allocation (jnxOperatingMemoryCP) and utilization(jnxOperatingBufferCP) in RE.
Added new offline reason vpnLocalizationRoleChange to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added MIBs for 1, 5 and 15 min average CPU util
Added new offline reasons fruFpcFanTrayIncompatible & fruFpcPEMIncompatible to jnxFruOfflineReason enumeration.
Added new color types for jnxLEDState and jnxLEDStateOrdered.
Added new trap: jnxFmAsicErr.
Added new FRU Power consumption variable.
Added new MIB jnxContentsModel.
Added new offline reason fruFpcHFanTrayIncompatible and missing entries mixedSwitchFabric, unsupportedFabric, jamConfigError.
Added new trap: jnxFmHealthChkErr.
Added new FRU type Fan Tray Controller.
Added new Added new OIDs to get memory utilization which doesn't include inactive memory as free memory
Added new offline reasons fruInvalidConfig, katsPostError and katsRuntimeError
Added new offline reasons gnfInitRestart and gnfOverlapMac
Added new offline reasons fpcUnsupportedMode
Added new offline reason fruOfflinedonFipsConstraints
Added new offline reasons fpcFtrayNotVerified, fpcPemNotVerified and fabricAsicFault
Added new Trap: jnxAlarmPortInput.
Added new offline reasons fruFpcSlcMisconfig, fruSfbFanTrayIncompatible and fruSfbPEMIncompatible
Added new FRU type Timing Interface Board.
